                    <locus target="#1r" facs="001">Fol. 1r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Face Plate pasted over the text: Yale University Library. Gideon Scull and Elizabeth Holmes Memorial. Gift of Edmund Wales Holmes, AB, MD. Class of 1872.  1920 [date of donation?]
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <locus target="#2r" facs="002">Fol. 2r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    contains a report, in German, of the contents and date of the book, in which the writer makes a case for the 17th century.  However, the Psalter is clearly written by a hand of the late-nineteenth or early-twentieth century
                    </desc>
                    </item>
